String.string: <font size='50'>Reinforcements approach. Don't let them overwhelm you!</font>
<font size='50'>Archers behind the bulwark! Take out the leaders!</font>
<font size='40'>The wardstone protects you from all damage for 20 seconds.</font>
<font size='40'>Rubinaria rushes to gather her young.</font>
<font size='50'>Smash the wardstone to prevent being overwhelmed.</font>
<font size='40'>Rubinaria weakens when her mate dies.</font>
<font size='40'>Namburus strengthens Rubinaria when he stands beside her.</font>
<font size='40'>Saravash will unleash his wrath in 15 minutes.</font>
<font size='40'>A caprin imp summons a spirit.</font>
<font size='50'>No more crystals will appear. Kill Saravash quickly.</font>
